%% ActivaClub - Logout Flow (AC-008)
%% Diagram 4 of 8
%% Last updated: 2026-04-05

sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant Zustand as Zustand Store
    participant MembersLambda
    participant Cognito

    User->>Frontend: Click "Cerrar sesión"
    Frontend->>MembersLambda: POST /v1/auth/logout (Authorization: Bearer AccessToken)

    alt Token already expired
        MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 401 TOKEN_EXPIRED
        Frontend->>Zustand: clearAuth() — clear tokens and user data
        Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /login
    end

    alt Network error
        MembersLambda-->>Frontend: Network failure
        Frontend->>Frontend: Show error message in Spanish
        Note over Frontend: Session preserved — store NOT cleared
    end

    MembersLambda->>Cognito: AdminUserGlobalSignOut { username }
    alt Cognito non-critical error
        Cognito-->>MembersLambda: Error
        MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 500 LOGOUT_FAILED
        Frontend->>Zustand: clearAuth()
        Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /login
    end

    Cognito-->>MembersLambda: OK (all active tokens invalidated)
    MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 200 { message: "Sesión cerrada correctamente" }
    Frontend->>Zustand: clearAuth() — clear tokens and user data
    Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /login

    Note over User,Cognito: Post-logout protection
    User->>Frontend: Navigate to protected route with old token
    Frontend->>MembersLambda: Any request with revoked AccessToken
    MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 401 (API Gateway JWT Authorizer rejects token)
    Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /login
